  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to determine whether a new method of enhancing and improving ECG
      acquisition, analysis and display is effective. The investigators will perform
      superimposition and summation of multiple standard ECG cycles, in the same lead, by temporal
      alignment to the peak R wave and voltage alignment to an improved baseline at the T-P
      segment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
